The paper deals with the capacity of a relay network, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and network optimization (cs.NI). The use of a polynomial-time algorithm suggests a focus on algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), while the use of submodularity and linear programming suggests a focus on optimization and machine learning (cs.SI, cs.LG).
